THESE INSTRUCTIONS NEED A LOT OF LOVE

The quickest way to install Mobile Web OSP is to do the following:

1. Copy the files to the final location on the server
2. Go to the command line
3. Type 'php setup.php' and follow the prompts
4. Set-up the apache config. You can use the example in the distribution.
5. Restart apache
6. Access your mobile host

You'll have to finish setting up each section by visiting http://mobilewebosp.pbworks.com/